social_posts.post_text:
Hello everyone my name is Dr.Anunya Reddy. 
With a passion for health care and dedication to improving lives I have embarked on fulfilling my journey as a doctor. 
I am a medical professional with degree of MBBS and MS ENT  head & neck surgery.
From diagnosing illness to providing compassionate care I strive to make a positive impact on well being of my patients.
My fascination for finer things and creativity with a background of head and neck surgery has led to my specialisation in facial plastic surgery.  Some of my patients were scared for surgical exploration so in the view of my patients interest I also specialised in non surgical cosmetology only to provide them with best option and care.
As a doctor my ultimate goal is to make a meaningful difference in the lives of my patients.
Thank you for taking the time to learn a little about me.
I look forward to connecting with you and contributing to your health care journey.
Stay healthy take care!!!
